# Investigation Hypothesis

## Primary Hypothesis
The user intentionally abused legitimate access to collect and stage sensitive data for unauthorized purposes.

## Alternative Hypotheses
- User credentials were compromised
- Activity caused by automated internal scripts
- Misconfigured permissions

## Validation Approach
- Correlate login activity with user schedule
- Review PowerShell command history
- Analyze file access frequency and scope

